{"tid":2454100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港台：過去24小時12人接種疫苗後送院　兩人留院觀察","createTime":"2021-03-20T03:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T03:49:21.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d847f89e4b2e88f84ce1659be615f9d582b8742","tid":2454100,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫苗接種計劃踏入第22日，過去24小時共有12宗送院個案，其中10宗已經出院，兩宗留院觀察。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗留院個案入院前，<strong>均曾接種復必泰疫苗</strong>，其中一宗個案是一名47歲男子，在龍琛路體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種疫苗，懷疑出現血管迷走神經性昏厥，送往北區醫院，情況穩定。另一名60歲女子，在東涌社區會堂社區疫苗接種中心接種疫苗後，感到胸部不適及血壓上升，送往北大嶼山醫院，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<strong>一名17歲男子在荃景圍體育館社區疫苗接種中心，接種復必泰疫苗後</strong>，感到腹痛及失去知覺，送往仁濟醫院，情況穩定，治療後毋須留院。<br />\n<br />\n今日8間社區疫苗接種中心之中，科興疫苗的整體接種率約84%，19間社區疫苗接種中心的復必泰疫苗的整體接種率約為96%。目前累計約30萬4100名市民已接種第一劑疫苗，其中約21萬3300人接種科興疫苗，約9萬800人接種復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581566-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581566-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=ab0183d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581566-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a48e10b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581566-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6c5b2210120d489005467e31e4f1fdbc4fdf7677","tid":2454100,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"［行動post］盧吉道要人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2454091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2454091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db65172c8e2201ca0045377737eb6e80d30b00fb","tid":2454100,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"失去知覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />17歲"}]}